 mental or physical?

222
00:11:08.209 --> 00:11:10.127
No. sir. it does not.

223
00:11:10.169 --> 00:11:13.214
Have you ever had             
      an unsatisfactory fitness     
      report. Commander Queeg?

224
00:11:13.255 --> 00:11:15.675
Negative. sir.

225
00:11:15.716 --> 00:11:19.845
Commander. can you account for    
 Lieutenant Maryk's opinion        
 that you were mentally ill?

226
00:11:19.887 --> 00:11:22.098
[chuckles]                    
      All I can say. sir.

