286
00:14:30.995 --> 00:14:32.371
Yes.

287
00:14:33.581 --> 00:14:35.290
Now. Lieutenant Keefer.

288
00:14:35.332 --> 00:14:37.877
were you serving          
          aboard the   Caine          
          in your present capacity

289
00:14:37.918 --> 00:14:40.129
on December 18th.     
              2022?                 
          Yes.

